high_descs: Turn right and move to the sink on the other side of the room.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Move a few inches to the right.
Slice up the tomato that's in the sink.
Set the knife down in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn left and move to the counter on the left of the stove.
Put the slice of tomato on the plate next to the stove.
Pick up the plate with tomato.
Move a few steps to the microwave on your left.
Put the plate into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato slice on a plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward to the shelves then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn right, walk one step forward and turn to face the sink.
Use the knife to chop up the tomato in the sink.
Put the knife down on the drain of the sink.
Pick up the middle piece of chopped up tomato.
Turn around and go to the white plate on the counter to the right.
Put the tomato slice on the left side of the plate.
Pick up the white plate from the counter.
Turn left, walk a step forward then face the oven and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the plate inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of sliced tomato on a white plate inside the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Go to the middle of the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the right of the stove
Put the tomato slice on the plate next to the stove
Pick up the plate
Go to the microwave
Put the plate in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a plated tomato slice in the microwave
